com.mapgroup.classificator.filemanager.writer

Class XlsWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapgroup.classificator.filemanager.writer.XlsWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataWriter

     class XlsWriter
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDataWriter
    Represents a way in order to generate a dataset representation using the Excel documents' format.

    Each dataset will be saved in the excel document in a single sheet which will be divided in this way:

    • attributes' name
    • attributes' type
    • dataset's content
